rows.label: tlk43420341_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Don't know why but there's something
really interesting about tending to trees.

rows.label: tlk43420341_02_msg0002
rows.name:
I see that you've spotted that
Vandham's hobby was growing trees.

rows.label: tlk43420341_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Seemed a waste to let them die, so
I've been taking care of them.

rows.label: tlk43420341_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Vandham was pretty special at growing
things - both people and trees.

rows.label: tlk43420341_02_msg0006
rows.name:
But you've got to keep moving forward.
That's what he would have wanted.
